cr3 \- program to view e-books (epub, fb2, html, txt, rtf...)
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B cr3
.RI [ options ] " filename"
.SH DESCRIPTION
This manual page documents briefly the
.B cr3
command.
.PP
.\" TeX users may be more comfortable with the \fB<whatever>\fP and
